2) Comply with sex offender registry and treatment;
3) Maintain full-time employment/schooling combination;
4) Have no contact with anyone under the age of 18 unless approved by agent;
5) Have no contact with the victim, W.E.D.;
6) Submit DNA sample and pay surcharge;
7) Pay costs of action; 
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
9) Spend six (6) months in jail, under the Huber Law, to commence on 02-02-16 at 5:00 p.m.
